cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep neural networks and their training using large datasets. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The approach proposed in the paper involves uncertainty estimation, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the use of ensembles is a common technique in neural networks (cs.NE).
